!**/.sops.yaml.example
**/profile.local.nix
!**/profile.local.nix.example
**/*.key
**/*.pem
**/*.p12
**/*.crt
**/*.env
**/.env
**/.env.*
**/api_key
**/.config/context7/
**/wireguard/
**/*_private_key*
**/tailscale_token
**/gatus_ssh_key

# Runtime secret paths (falls je ins Workspace kopiert)
**/var/lib/secrets/

